thread.title: Phil B
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Phil B

author: Phil B
title: Phil B
text:
Item was way cheaper than the bricks and mortar competitor, arrived when I needed it (asap) and delivery information was reliably transferred to the courier. Well done. Will use again next time.
Would love for them to be able to source non-Australian printer ink (Epson stylus PX650) as I have to buy from a UK site. Otherwise 5 stars.
